                  "revisionId": 2696108,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Keep in mind that Diriga will use this precept regardless of the weapon equipped , which has interesting consequences with certain weapons;"
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
